Paper: hep-th/9507152

Date: 1995-07-27

Title: Bosonization of Fermion Determinants

Comments: 9 pages, latex, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B366 (1996) 253-260

A four dimensional fermion determinant is presented as a path integral of theexponent of a local five dimensional action describing constrained bosonicsystem. The construction is carried out both in the continuum theory and in thelattice model.